text: Let's face it, it's a $10 per night hostel in Singapore. It is seedy, not the cleanest place in the world, and the bathroom would be disgusting by many people's standards. But it is just a 10-minute walk to the MRT so easy access to the airport.
Cheap hostel with a kitchen and common area. A bit dark with no natural light and out of the city centre in Singapore but good in comparison to others in Singapore for the price you pay.
The room was always dirty and no cleaning service
